# FILE: productDetail.desc
# ROLE: Technical Spec-Sheet & Transaction Terminal
# VIBE: Data-Heavy / Industrial Precision / High-Trust

## A. THE HERO SPLIT (60/40 Layout)
- **LEFT (GALLERY):** - Vertical thumbnail strip + Large Main View. 
    - **FEATURE:** Includes "Zoom-on-Hover" to inspect hardware condition (crucial for used/broker items).
- **RIGHT (THE BUY BOX):**
    - **TITLE & ID:** Laptop ThinkPad X1 | #HS-102.
    - **STATUS PULSE:** [ ✅ متوفر حالياً ] or [ ⏳ قيد التأمين ].
    - **PRICE TERMINAL:** Large font showing the "Student Saving" amount.
    - **PRIMARY ACTION:** [ 💳 حجز وإتمام الدفع ].

## B. THE "LOGISTICS & TRUST" BENTO
- **SOURCE BOX:** - If [ 🏠 منصة ]: "هذا المنتج مملوك للمنصة وموجود في مستودعاتنا."
    - If [ 🤝 وسيط ]: "توفير خارجي: يتم تأمين المنتج عبر شركاء المنصة مع فحص فني كامل."
- **DELIVERY BOX:** Admin-controlled text (e.g., "استلام من مكتب الهندسة المعمارية").
- **WARRANTY BOX:** Terms of testing (e.g., "3 days money-back if hardware fails").

## C. THE "TECHNICAL DNA" (FULL SPECS)
- **FORMAT:** A clean, monospace table or grid.
- **DATA:** CPU, RAM, GPU, Battery Health, Port Selection, Weight.
- **ATTACHMENT:** Link to "Download Official Datasheet (PDF)" if available.

## D. THE ADMIN OVERRIDE (STICKY)
- **LOGIC:** If the logged-in user is `Role: Admin`, show an [ ✏️ Edit Product ] floating button that links directly to the Admin Panel for this specific ID.